                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77 Chinese Eastern/193: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-08-09T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 9, 1929—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>263. Your 688, August 8, 7 p.m. The Department feels that the sending of such a
                    note at this time would only further cloud the situation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cotton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
